# The contact form submits to a Cloudflare Pages Function at /api/contact.
# No environment variables are required locally.
#
# For production, set the following as a Cloudflare Pages secret:
#
#   RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
#
# Add it via the Cloudflare dashboard:
#   Pages → noku-labs → Settings → Environment variables → Add secret
#
# The domain nokulabs.com must be verified in Resend before emails will send.
